            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The <strong class="text-slate-200">debt snowball vs avalanche calculator</strong> debate is one of personal finance's most enduring discussions — and the answer genuinely depends on whether you optimize for mathematics or motivation.
